# 🚗 Vehicle Rental System (C++ OOP Project)

## 📌 Overview

This is a simple Vehicle Rental System built using C++ and
Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts.\
The project simulates renting and returning vehicles such as cars and
bikes.

## ⚙️ Features

-   Add vehicles (Car & Bike)
-   Display available vehicles
-   Rent a vehicle
-   Return a vehicle
-   Calculate rental cost

## 🧠 OOP Concepts Used

-   Inheritance
-   Polymorphism
-   Encapsulation
-   Abstraction

## ▶️ How to Run

Compile: g++ main.cpp -o rental

Run: ./rental

